StorageAccess - Class in com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.notinuse
Deprecated.
This class was used to access the storage of the app. It is not used in the final application. The Storage Access Class had to be replaced because it implemented the DataFetcher and DataSender interfaces. These interfaces were replaced with the middle man.
